  <p class="mb-6">
    Funded Elite allows you to fully customise your challenge account plan on their web page. You can set scalping permissions, weekend trading add-on, leverage for FX (1:30, 1:50, or 1:100), profit split (60%, 70%, 80%, or 95%), and days between payouts (3, 7, 14, or 21 days). The first payout is always after 21 days regardless of the interval selected at checkout.
